\title{aisstream: Live Vessel-Tracking Stream Client for AISStream.io}
\description{
A thin R client for the AISStream.io live vessel-tracking WebSocket feed, built on connectcore. Open one socket, subscribe with bounding boxes plus optional MMSI / message-type filters, and handle raw frames Node-ws style. Reconnect, re-subscribe, keepalive and a watchdog are inherited; the message hot path is parse-free so the vendor never drops a slow reader, and parse helpers plus a durable NDJSON recorder are included.
